&lt;p&gt;Our Pharmacy Operations Associate Program is a structured, full-time, rotational program designed for individuals interested in launching a career in healthcare and pharmacy services. Over the course of the program, you will rotate through key operational areas within BlinkRx’s closed-door pharmacy operations. In each rotation you will learn critical business functions and skill sets while getting hands-on experience, mentorship, and the opportunity to contribute meaningfully to our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Upon successful completion of the program, you will be placed in a full-time role within the department that best matches your skills, interests, and organizational needs.&lt;/p&gt;
