&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior Authorization Support: Complete and submit prior authorization forms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provider/Patient/Insurer Communications: Conduct outbound calls with patients, providers, and insurers to resolve routine and new issues with patients, doctors and insurers&lt;/li&gt;
