&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network Strategy &amp;amp; Performance Architecture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and refine the operating model for BlinkRx’s national pharmacy network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define performance frameworks across cost, service levels, scalability, and risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify structural improvement opportunities through data-driven analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead executive-level business reviews focused on strategic optimization and long-term partnership evolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate insights into clear action plans with measurable impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Functional Leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product, Engineering, Revenue, Finance, Legal, and Patient Services to drive complex initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Convert ambiguous business problems into structured workstreams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure network considerations are embedded in product design and growth planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive initiatives end-to-end — from hypothesis through implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Partner Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a senior point of contact for key pharmacy partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Elevate relationships from transactional to strategic and performance-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate negotiations, incentive alignment, and contractual discussions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance partner collaboration with performance accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
